import React, { useState } from 'react';

export default function (props) {   

    console.log(props)
    return (

                </View>

                <View style={styles.tablePODMedicoesRow4}>

'18' : (props.tipoClasse == false && props.tipoCurvaOuTangente  == 'tangente') ? '34' : (props.tipoClasse == true && props.tipoCurvaOuTangente  == 'curva') ? '14' : (props.tipoClasse == true && props.tipoCurvaOuTangente  == 'tangente') ? '47' : ''}</Text>

                <View style={styles.tablePODMedicoesRow4}>

                </View>
